          <a href="https://fox8.com/news/local/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fox 8</a>
          <a href="https://www.wkyc.com/local" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WKYC</a>
          <a href="https://signalcleveland.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Signal Cleveland</a>
          <a href="https://thelandcle.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Land</a>
          <a href="https://eyeonohio.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Eye on Ohio</a>
          <a href="https://www.clevescene.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cleveland Scene</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </noscript>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="news-cta" aria-labelledby="news-cta-heading">
  <div class="news-cta-inner">
    <h2 id="news-cta-heading">¿Te Importa Lo Que Pasa Aquí?</h2>
    <p>Ayuda a Cortney a ganar un lugar en la boleta. Cada firma acerca la representación impulsada por el pueblo a la realidad.</p>
